metadata.name: 白昼夢の女の子
metadata.description:
DayDream Girls Collections

The girl named Saho is a person with supernatural power to manipulate the gravity of space to achieve its purpose, but the girl at her childhood found its ability by humans and often detained in the laboratory until the age of 17, humans loaded her into a spacerocket was launched into space, after the successful launch and fully docked successfully as a space station, humans use brain interface to send data to its brain and control its ability to make the space station to complete the rotation, in the cold experimental tank The girl can only pray and dream.....

[3112 x 4842]
